title: Stop Doing These 4 Things If You Want to Be Happy
itunes:title: Stop Doing These 4 Things If You Want to Be Happy
description:
Episode 557 - Happiness is not really that hard to understand is it? Stop doing the things you hate doing and do more of the stuff you love doing, right? If it were that easy, everyone would be happy! It seems there is more to be said than just that, so in this episode I talk about the 4 things you should stop doing right now if you want to be happy.
